# Portfolio Project Structure & Architecture

This repository is a modern Next.js 15 portfolio website built with TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and shadcn/ui components.

## Core Stack
- Framework: Next.js 15 with App Router
- Language: TypeScript (strict)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS v4
- UI Components: shadcn/ui with Radix UI primitives
- Content: MDX (with math via KaTeX)
- Deployment: Vercel

## Key Directories
- `src/app/` – App Router pages and layouts
- `src/components/` – Reusable React components
- `src/components/ui/` – shadcn/ui base components
- `src/data/` – Data layer (resume data, blog utilities)
- `src/lib/` – Utility functions and configurations
- `content/` – MDX blog posts and content
- `content/zh/` – Chinese language content
- `public/` – Static assets and images

